*moreutils-0.44 (29 Mar 2011)

  29 Mar 2011; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> -moreutils-0.40.ebuild,
  -moreutils-0.42.ebuild, moreutils-0.43.ebuild, +moreutils-0.44.ebuild:
  Version bump and remove old. Add dependency on dev-perl/IPC-Run (bug #358751
  by Siim Ainsaar) and temporarily drop ~hppa keyword.

